    ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║   Stellar UI Library  —  v3.0  (Major Architecture Overhaul)║
    ║   Original: Friskl  |  Overhaul v2.0  |  Rewrite v3.0       ║
    ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    CHANGELOG (v3.0 — Full Rewrite):

    ── ARCHITECTURE ────────────────────────────────────────────────
    • Signal class  — replaces raw listener tables; :Fire/:Connect/:Once/:Destroy
    • ComponentRegistry — components self-register on creation, O(1) theme updates
      (eliminates the costly O(n) full-descendant sweep on every theme change)
    • Config validator — warns with source on missing required Cfg fields
    • Scoped Maid — each component gets its own child Maid, not just per-window

    ── THEMES ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    • New "Midnight" theme  — deep navy with neon-blue accent
    • New "Sakura" theme    — soft pink/peach light mode
    • Gradient accent tokens added (AccentGradStart / AccentGradEnd)
    • Glow color token (AccentGlow) for pulsing effects
    • All four themes: Dark · Light · Midnight · Sakura

    ── ANIMATION SYSTEM ────────────────────────────────────────────
    • SpringTween() — simple spring physics (stiffness / damping) via Heartbeat
    • Easing presets: Quart, Sine, Back, Bounce exposed as named constants
    • Ripple() — circular ink-ripple on button press (pure Instance, no assets)
    • PulseGlow() — accent-glow pulse on any frame (UIStroke thickness wave)
    • Animations:SlideIn() / SlideOut() — directional slide helpers

    ── NEW COMPONENTS ──────────────────────────────────────────────
    • AddNumberInput()   — labelled ± stepper, min/max/step, scrollwheel support
    • AddRadioGroup()    — mutually exclusive option set (replaces multi-toggle pattern)
    • AddSearchDropdown()— dropdown with live search/filter textbox
    • AddTooltip()       — hover tooltip attached to any component
    • AddBadge()         — numeric / text badge on a Tab button
    • AddTagRow()        — horizontal chip/tag strip with add/remove
    • AddSwitch()        — iOS-style pill switch (alias of Toggle with new visual)
    • AddConfirmButton() — two-stage "click → confirm" button
    • AddNotification()  — enhanced; accepts Type (info/success/warning/error)
                           with inline icon, progress bar, action button

    ── COMPONENT API IMPROVEMENTS ──────────────────────────────────
    • All Add* now return an enriched control with :Destroy() to remove themselves
    • Toggle / Slider / Keybind / Dropdown — all support :OnChanged(fn) via Signal
    • Input — Cfg.Validator: function(str) → bool | string (error message)
    • Input — Cfg.Mask: pattern to strip invalid chars on each keystroke
    • Slider — click anywhere on track to jump; scroll-wheel ±step support
    • Slider — Cfg.Suffix/Prefix for display (e.g. "100 ms", "$5.00")
    • Dropdown — Cfg.Searchable flag → enables built-in search box
    • Dropdown — auto-closes on click outside (UserInputService global listener)
    • Keybind — Cfg.AllowMouse: accept mouse buttons as keybinds
    • NumberInput — scroll wheel supported; hold Shift for 10× step

    ── WINDOW API ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
    • Window:SetTab(name)            — unchanged
    • Window:AddTabBadge(tab,n)      — set badge count on tab button
    • Window:ClearTabBadge(tab)      — remove badge
    • Window:SetVisible(bool)        — unchanged
    • Window:SetTitle(str)           — live title update
    • Window:SetSubtitle(str)        — live subtitle update
    • Window:OnThemeChanged(fn)      — unchanged; fn(mode,theme)
    • Window:Destroy()               — full teardown (unchanged)
    • Window:Toast(Cfg)              — fire a notification (alias)

    ── PERFORMANCE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
    • ComponentRegistry replaces O(n) sweep: registered slots updated directly
    • Slider Heartbeat replaced with InputChanged poll — no frame-skip jitter
    • Dropdown items built lazily; search filter runs on pre-built list
    • task.spawn guards replaced with pcall + task.spawn for crash isolation

    ── MOBILE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    • Swipe left/right for tab navigation (unchanged, improved threshold)
    • Long-press on a Toggle also fires its callback (vibration-ready hook)
    • Touch targets consistently ≥ 44 px height (WCAG mobile guideline)

    ── BUG FIXES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
    • Dropdown: previous close delay was 0.3 s → now driven by animation done
    • Slider: mouse drag now also tracks when cursor leaves the track area
    • ColorPicker: SVDragging / HueDragging properly cancelled on window close
    • Toggle: rapid double-click no longer desynchronises Value.Value
    • Keybind: Listening guard extended — now uses debounce not bool flag
    • Notifications: z-ordering fixed so toasts always appear above the window

]]


